  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "You are proficient at dodging blows.\nPrerequisite: Dex 13, Dodge.\nBenefit: You must be psionically focused to use this feat. You receive a +1 dodge bonus to your Armor Class. This bonus stacks with the bonus from the Dodge feat (but only applies on attacks made by the opponent you have designated).",
